{"tid":645163,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母邊條柒頭皮係poly搞自助收餐具","createTime":"2018-04-28T01:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T06:32:42.000Z","uid":33788,"like":8,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"238d291c42a1e4ae406b04f67730e04d62d629f7","tid":645163,"uid":33788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:02:53.000Z","msg":"迫啲比左錢買服務買野食既學生幫大財團cut cost賺多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔見你玩自助夾餸？<br />\n<br />\n水機隔離應該扮支洗潔精呀嘛<br />\n反撚正啲刀刀叉叉都冇撚洗過咁<br />\n隻匙羹有幾pat漬都照擺出黎扮洗左 仆你個街由其戇鳩新can"},{"pid":"f7f2363d62b29db61fbf7b244be413e4ce09e59c","tid":645163,"uid":69013,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:05:36.000Z","msg":"大部分大學都係咁 <br />\n如果你有留意，同一集團同一個餐出面貴過大學，係因為大學收平租，要求減價，同樣少左人收餐具，減左成本都會回饋俾學生。"},{"pid":"ac3063af15d1bb99805898e1f85dde5aff4a9d28","tid":645163,"uid":134171,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:12:52.000Z","msg":"唔係好多大學都係自助㗎咩？"},{"pid":"4184613807e6ad947fd7e50be306da1e15d860c7","tid":645163,"uid":33788,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7f2363d62b29db61fbf7b244be413e4ce09e59c","tid":645163,"uid":69013,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:05:36.000Z","msg":"大部分大學都係咁 <br />\n如果你有留意，同一集團同一個餐出面貴過大學，係因為大學收平租，要求減價，同樣少左人收餐具，減左成本都會回饋俾學生。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"減兩條友既人工可以回饋到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最撚嘔心係前排貼係民主牆，講到啲餐具擺係度無人執係學生問題咁"},{"pid":"2340770442d78137ab114d2a2f058044b0fb62f8","tid":645163,"uid":34942,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"人就得一個<br />\n食呢就幾廿個 <br />\n點執得曬呀 食完咪順手擺返好囉 好嘥你時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比嗰啲啲錢想要有咩服務呀 <br />\n使唔使同你做埋腳底按摩呀"},{"pid":"a48774e4209ee50878370857e64289d06501f880","tid":645163,"uid":77484,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"784cb9c52e2f61d57ee0842e2615c74305df0b4c","tid":645163,"uid":102187,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:25:01.000Z","msg":"aggr<br />\n重點係大財團 唔係小本經營喎<br />\n如果唔係好賺佢一定唔會bid<br />\n咁佢請多幾個都係幾皮野<br />\n增加就業機會先係回饋社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e627c75555e687e48e624107e76dd37f11a9c3de","tid":645163,"uid":111241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"你咁撚介意咪出去食囉 仲有靚can都can 再唔係外賣"},{"pid":"e620f56b231c6f2e66449d5a22fc7542691ea19d","tid":645163,"uid":24378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:31:09.000Z","msg":"呢樣嘢實行咗好多年啦，大學飯堂咁多人，自己食完自己放返去個架到好難為你咩？<br />\n咁樣成個飯堂運作係最快，食完下手可以即刻坐低食，做大學生畀返少少責任感啦，俾少少錢使唔使餵埋你食抹埋咀？不如帶埋老豆老母嚟同你返學服侍你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e35c28fe8df5b1e475864500606c68f1476e98","tid":645163,"uid":33788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a48774e4209ee50878370857e64289d06501f880","tid":645163,"uid":77484,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"我次次都唔該前唔該後<br />\n<br />\n上面講一個人一對手做唔哂<br />\n唔見間大財團請多個人??<br />\n一唔係就加我價囉 反正唔係冇加過<br />\n<br />\n你根本唔係幫緊個姐姐 <br />\n係幫緊個財團<br />\n你估佢執少左碟代表佢整體工作量會下降?<br />\n屌啦星成班係度以為自己幫左人係度自high<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係想幫人既就直接同財團傾啦<br />\n叫佢加兩蚊價請多兩條友 加人工"},{"pid":"66ad09b5a3f53abd45bb11c8564aecbe2caa0043","tid":645163,"uid":4070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a292562c1395df2627a384659ce8f338e295d8f8","tid":645163,"uid":33788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e620f56b231c6f2e66449d5a22fc7542691ea19d","tid":645163,"uid":24378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:31:09.000Z","msg":"呢樣嘢實行咗好多年啦，大學飯堂咁多人，自己食完自己放返去個架到好難為你咩？<br />\n咁樣成個飯堂運作係最快，食完下手可以即刻坐低食，做大學生畀返少少責任感啦，俾少少錢使唔使餵埋你食抹埋咀？不如帶埋老豆老母嚟同你返學服侍你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野LOGIC<br />\n食完野執碟倒垃圾=有責任感?<br />\n又唔見洗豌個個比啲責任感?<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你去出面啲餐廳會自己執?<br />\n你食完個M記係照鳩擺係度啦<br />\n你夠可以幫佢倒落垃圾桶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為佢比出面平左兩蚊所以我就變左唔負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有polyu係今日朝早先出現呢舊野<br />\n我可能講得唔清楚<br />\n唔係食完拎走個盤<br />\n而係食完拎走自己倒湯倒垃圾再分類<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今朝我見到啲人食完個面係度倒湯倒到隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91971d4db4bafddd18afda3cdc83400336b2545","tid":645163,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2340770442d78137ab114d2a2f058044b0fb62f8","tid":645163,"uid":34942,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"人就得一個<br />\n食呢就幾廿個 <br />\n點執得曬呀 食完咪順手擺返好囉 好嘥你時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonde